title: Rampal & Ristenpart : Handel, Bach, Vivaldi, Tartini
description:
French flutist J.P Rampal and Conductor Ristenpart play : 

Vivaldi : concerto RV 103
Handel : "Hallenser" sonatas (Harpsichord : Veyron-Lacroix)
Bach : cantata BWV 209 and concerto BWV 1056 (!)
Tartini : concerto in G minor

Recordings are old, so sometimes the sound is a bit dirty (particularly on the cantata)... But Rampal still plays GREAT ! 

All tracks : mp3, 320kbps

Enjoy !
